d style=\"min-width: 80px; height: 120px; border: 1px solid black!important;\"></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_line\">\n                    A to oznacza, że jest\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">&gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;</div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\\(6+6+6+3\\) szukanych liczb</div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\\(6\\cdot 6\\cdot 6\\cdot 3\\) szukanych liczb</div>\n<div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">zatwierdź</div>.\n                </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n                Szukanych liczb parzystych jest\n                \\[\n                6\\cdot 6\\cdot 6\\cdot 3=648\n                \\]\n            </div>\n</div>\n"
